{"tid":462173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺啲廢老成日叫人孝順好撚戇鳩？","createTime":"2017-11-08T10:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T18:13:15.000Z","uid":157304,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a70f02419aa569185f702f2141b97132da41ef4a","tid":462173,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"一個人值得俾人尊重嘅話<br />\n人哋自己會尊重佢㗎啦<br />\n關個人有冇血緣同年紀大乜嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3993324c1fb449126beae3b1f479ca503a91183c","tid":462173,"uid":157304,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:14:18.000Z","msg":"仲有啲傻閪話揀老公一定要孝順<br />\n咁先係好仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嫁著個冇思考能力嘅裙腳仔<br />\n遲下又婆媳糾紛我真係恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3df7f4ca36eb854628daff767d5ef4a7e4d57e","tid":462173,"uid":27729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"孝順同讓座都係發自內心<br />\n下下叫人做 完全扭曲左原本既意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8dd3ff92b484102360ad50194a3f9e9d50d1b49","tid":462173,"uid":157304,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孝順同讓座都係發自內心<br />\n下下叫人做 完全扭曲左原本既意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<br />\n值得人尊重嘅話根本唔使同人乞"},{"pid":"56c9c532e823eb1b2b70716fc8b5fae672b5e83c","tid":462173,"uid":93202,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:54:30.000Z","msg":"就係佢地自知唔值得比人孝順咁對待咪成日提醒人要對佢好囉<br />\n講埋d咩佢係你邊個邊個所以你更加要孝順佢<br />\n我屌你啦<br />\n你點對我我點對你架啦 孝你老母閪咩"},{"pid":"ff90dadf7bb46b2e947b8072e0260e98c6fcdb03","tid":462173,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"有d廢老根本冇撚用 , 留o係世上獻世<br />\n為左拎番少少存在感咪叫人地尊重佢 <br />\n本質上其實係白白消耗地球資源既垃圾"},{"pid":"1ce796fd3e2bc57a38e840de078031ef6d7df86e","tid":462173,"